gy, Anthropology, Computer Music, and History of Science.&nbsp;</p>"}],"speaker_name":"Daniel Levitin","tags":["brain","health","mental health","neuroscience","memory","cognitive science","medicine"],"title":"How to stay calm when you know you'll be stressed","video_type":{"id":"1","name":"TED Stage Talk"},"viewed_count":11667461}]}
